divs: Sighting Detailsmy wife and i were having lunch outside a restaurant in kearny mesa looked straight up and saw a disk moving across the sky near the moon it appeared to have orange tint we both were just looking up staring i suppose in disbelief (i asked my wife if she was seeing what i was seeing and she said yes) the object was very high in altitude and moving across thesky near the moon, i got up when i realized we had a camera in the car when i returned it was gone what did we see? .
